{"tid":684822,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"迪士尼開拍《黑魔后2》","createTime":"2018-05-31T01:53:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T04:05:13.000Z","uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0be9d39cda26cdced4093511ce92f8ddc1b93adb","tid":684822,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T01:53:43.000Z","msg":"女星安祖蓮娜祖莉(Angelina Jolie)同畢彼特(Brad Pitt)離婚，又轉做幕後監製電影，近幾年已甚少見到佢幕前演出。好彩迪士尼夠「牙力」，安祖蓮娜終於肯拍《黑魔后》(Maleficent)第2集。片中飾演安祖蓮娜囡囡嘅女星艾麗芬寧(Elle Fanning)喺Instagram放咗2張自拍相，第1張係艾麗背後有對角伸出嚟，唔知係邊位喎! 第2張終於開估，原來係安祖蓮娜開心「攝位」嘅成功合照。艾麗留言 : 「帶媽媽去拍攝《黑魔后》嘅日子」。兩母女好sweet呀!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2018/5/1527673663_ql-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2018%2F5%2F1527673663_ql-1280w.jpg&h=f8844d6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2018/5/1527673671_iY-1280w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2018%2F5%2F1527673671_iY-1280w.jpg&h=6774125a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"82c0bab30f923969ef8abbfddcb5e448016bbe44","tid":684822,"uid":105605,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T04:05:13.000Z","msg":"幾好睇"}]}